This will sometimes make kinda funny effects, pets often have higher agro when the melee standing close, so it is not totaly uncommen mobs summon pets instead of lowagro melee even if both fighting them.<br>
<br>
DS itself add no extra agro, the only agro you get from a DS is if the mage try to cast it on someone already agroed on a mob (this can be yourself just inside proximity of a kos mob). But this is true for every buffs, test this, go to N Tov, wait until someone pull a drake (must be kos), get close to the drake, invis yourself (or any other targeted buff) and you will get a factionhit, selfonly buffs not counting. This is way giving a modrod during a fight will sometimes give you a factionhit, and if you want to avoid factionhits in Tov, always DS before the pull.<br>
<br>
There also a huge between mobs when they will be able to summon. IV is a good example, archers can acctaully take of 3-4% of him before he be able to start summon, snakes in Ssra on the other hand will start summon after they hit a DS once (always pull with malise, I got summoned once with a cast of Burst of flame).<br>
<br>
An other thing to prove that DS add 0 agro, DS yourself, go to Commons, sit down in an Orc camp, watch the whole camp kill themself on your DS (do not hit back, have pet or nuke) every single orc will just depop give no faction, no corpse, this happens because no dmg was done that could count toward a specific player.<br>
<br>
There also other aspects to gaining agro, if a mob agro you, but it can't reach you for some reason (rooted or pathing issues) it still will keep track of what you doing and you will gain tons of agro. <br>
One example to test this, have a druid kite around something in GD giants wars, and kite to close to spearmens, that druid will not think anything about it, he will heal, buff and whatever, the moment someone hurt that spearman, guess who it will summon ..  the druid, and in many cases that spearman wont stop summon the poor druid until either one of them is dead. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=drokaten>drokaten</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 32<br> <font color=#333333>(12/24/02 9:06:13 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm29.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=907.topic&index=23>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: PoP pets VS Epic and agro on multiple mobs</span><hr size=1> o i see what you meant.. if you weren't so hot to flame.. you'd realize that i had started to say 'i never said' then realized i had IN FACT said that.. so modified my 5th post to say 'on a pull'<br>
