<br>
A mob can summon if it is damaged beyond a certain percent of it's hp. It does not matter how it took that damage.<br>
<br>
Damage shields do not generate agro.<br>
<br>
The casting of a damage shield can generate a bit of agro toward the caster, just as any buff will.<br>
<br>
There is no reason to believe that the epic pet taunts any better than the new pets.<br>
